Before Bookstaver, Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Catharine Sheridan, Respondent, v. William Scott, Appellant. Appeal from judgment in favor of the plaintiff, en-, tered upon a verdict, and from order denying motion for a new trial. Charles C. Nadal, for appellant. John A. Duti ton, for respondent.

Judgment affirmed.
